{
  "name": "davepi-plugin-skill-extractor",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "The learning loop for @davepi/agent: resolved conversations are queued to a fresh extraction agent that proposes reusable runbooks as governed draft skills (a human approves before they reach the prompt). Subscribes to conversation.resolved on the record bus and runs off-thread via davepi-plugin-queue.",
